{"tid":863434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［的士司機案］專家證人指警員繞頸致頸椎移位 警方律師：專家係'醫管局主席' 信醫護人員冇做錯先咁講","createTime":"2018-10-15T14:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T14:38:13.000Z","uid":48083,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"95a15caa536637d2c771cfc67c11ddafc99c21b9","tid":863434,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:56:15.000Z","msg":"65歲的士司機因車資問題與乘客爭執而被捕，被帶上警車時遭警員箍頸及扯高離地，頸椎移位，留院一個月後不治。<span style=\"color: red;\">專家證人相信司機遭警員以手繞頸部扯至雙腳離地，被兩股分別向上及下墜力量拉扯，致令司機頸椎移位。</span>專家證人作供完畢後特意慰問死者家屬，希望家屬能「走出哀痛，好好生活」。遺孀聞言哭泣及點頭，家屬律師亦向專家表達深深感激。<br />\n<br />\n事發於2012年11月11日晚上近10時，死者陳輝旺（65歲）在西隧行政大樓附近遭警方拘捕，同晚送院，翌月12日死亡。法醫指發現死者患有心臟病，事發後長期卧床，其後出現心肺功能障礙。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">身為獨立專家證人的醫管局骨科中央統籌委員會主席李淵粦今早重申，警員林偉榮用手環繞司機頸部，將司機向上拉扯上警車，令司機雙腳離地，另有力量向下墜，且司機頭部旋轉90度，這些外力令司機頸椎第5及6節移位。<br />\n<br />\n指司機遭警箍頸後 「變咗另一個人，冇晒抗爭意識」<br />\n<br />\n李又解釋，司機被警員用手環繞頸後頸椎小節移位，「變咗另一個人，冇晒抗爭意識」，不能在警車內端坐，而頸椎移位令司機脊髓受壓，司機起初四肢仍有力，但會覺得頸痛及麻痺，及後身體情況在惡性循環下一路差下去。<br />\n</span><br />\n代表「箍頸警」林偉榮的大律師今早盤問李醫生時指出，司機送院期間及入院初期，沒有向救護人員稱頸痛，那是否有可能司機感覺不到頸痛。李解釋，病人的臨床病徵及身體變化並不同步，需要醫生不斷檢查；司機亦有可能因服用了止痛藥阿司匹靈，才沒有向醫護人員透露頸痛。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">該大律師繼而指李醫生是「醫管局主席」，李是在深信醫管局職員沒有犯錯的前設下，才會指司機是入院前已頸椎受傷。</span><span style=\"color: red;\">李醫生回答有關提問時頗為「勞氣」，堅稱絕不懷疑司機的病人排板紀錄出現造假問題，又糾正「箍頸警」大律師的錯誤，強調：「醫管局主席係梁智仁教授，我只係醫管局轄下小小骨科中央統籌委員會主席。做呢個主席要有經驗同無私，如果覺得專家證人有偏袒，請你馬上請佢離開！」</span><br />\n<br />\n質疑警員說法 「一個人俯臥踢腳，有幾傷害？」<br />\n<br />\n醫管局大律師亦認為這是十分嚴重的指控，質疑「箍頸警」的大律師指控專家證人偏頗時，手握甚麼證據以作出指控。「箍頸警」的大律師遂澄清並非指控，僅是疑問而已。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一名警員馬振康，閉路電視影片顯示司機被帶上警車後，馬兩度走上警車。馬早前作供時指司機踢腳，他因擔心死者踢到警長，才上車按住司機的腳。李醫生不認同馬的說法，指司機當時俯臥車內，質疑：「一個人俯臥踢腳，有幾傷害？」<br />\n<br />\n李醫生作供完畢後，特意向家屬表示，對於司機不能逆轉的頸傷，他深感遺憾，惟望家屬能「走出哀痛，好好生活」。遺孀聞言立即哭泣及點頭，女兒在旁輕輕拍背安慰。代表家屬的資深大律師蘇朗年亦向李醫生表達深深感激。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：CCDI477/13】<br />\n<br />\n記者戴國輝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181015/58796597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181015%2F58796597&d=SzeCi%2Frp0vCg6CgE8yKKz9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=bf1b78b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181015%2F58796597&h=259a412c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181015/58796597</a>"},{"pid":"caf1d7e190d8d1ad630986d66123b33b88e3f875","tid":863434,"uid":61271,"like":124,"dislike":3,"score":121,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲律師真係仆街<br />\n<br />\n比我就串鳩番佢收左警方錢先會埋沒良心咁幫黑警辯護，睇佢點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad5255d5fdbf3771d42006d017cbeb3de12995a","tid":863434,"uid":54876,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"推到入誤殺"},{"pid":"3d5f0e2d4ffb7ba6b11aeea8c93d50c94fc03675","tid":863434,"uid":195944,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"bad5255d5fdbf3771d42006d017cbeb3de12995a","tid":863434,"uid":54876,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"推到入誤殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"人地養鬼仔 邊會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1ecb52f0d478b7ec561d938244a32edf4471f3","tid":863434,"uid":195944,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"病人排板紀錄出現造假問題。。。。<br />\n<br />\n個個好似黑警咁咩 字又唔識多隻 又無常識 又無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ce14bddab949390a4c1f3adfe01c8297293fa5","tid":863434,"uid":34410,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"d警犬真係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ecb6072b8d1518bea6132578bd3bc64f5b6808","tid":863434,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:24:49.000Z","msg":"訴諸動機謬論"},{"pid":"7f7fcafb46cf73b4ad6c68047419b6fd6db4e585","tid":863434,"uid":119895,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"根本可以告班黑警酷刑罪"},{"pid":"a176db9893130675873d4c20cb3009b53edef409","tid":863434,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad15f41f61576e3e9344d227a868e1fda335bb73","tid":863434,"uid":8880,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街差佬一定要挫死佢 咁樣箍頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be60b16f759d4dc8bcc7fe68654cb7dcab344e22","tid":863434,"uid":90820,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「箍頸警」的大律師遂澄清並非指控，僅是疑問而已。</blockquote><br />\n彈出又彈入<br />\n講完就收返當無數<br />\n淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dc156f4635c2577a2d78512436daefc37317b0","tid":863434,"uid":90820,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"caf1d7e190d8d1ad630986d66123b33b88e3f875","tid":863434,"uid":61271,"like":124,"dislike":3,"score":121,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲律師真係仆街<br />\n<br />\n比我就串鳩番佢收左警方錢先會埋沒良心咁幫黑警辯護，睇佢點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驛站原則(Cab Rank Rule)為法律界專業守則之一，亦稱不得拒聘原則，在這原則下，執業大律師接到案件後，除非存在利益衝突，否則若能處理該案件而當事人亦能付出適當費用時，大律師都必須摒棄對當事人或其訟因的喜惡，代其出庭訟辯。此原則可確保不會有人因為不受歡迎或因不得人心而不能覓得法律代表。</blockquote><br />\n個律師都無得揀客嘅<br />\n專業守則嚟<br />\n不過兜得樣衰囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a15f283b8dba4557853bfecec6efd2404fa11a5","tid":863434,"uid":83344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"隻隻狗都諗住攞正牌打9人，個犯殘廢咪話係意外囉"},{"pid":"268cb4f1bde701f2bf3c6e4909b3220d869dfe69","tid":863434,"uid":14433,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"陰功，好地地一個人俾警察整死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲講到好似警察唔洗負責任咁"},{"pid":"f756c9d9816cbb9259e7c4ab06e35f2e3ad2e12d","tid":863434,"uid":61271,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"除非黑警有專家證人證明佢咁cool頸都無問題，單憑一條律師仔可以鋤散一個專家醫生既醫學專業證供？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如無意外今次死因庭既結論一定係黑警使用過份武力導致死者重傷，間接導致死亡<br />\n但死因庭係唔會對警員作出訴訟<br />\n需要警方搜證同律政司落charge <br />\n<br />\n唉，又唔知要等幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308013757b7b6a5ab5cb24182bc8329409af9abe","tid":863434,"uid":61271,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"86dc156f4635c2577a2d78512436daefc37317b0","tid":863434,"uid":90820,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"caf1d7e190d8d1ad630986d66123b33b88e3f875","tid":863434,"uid":61271,"like":124,"dislike":3,"score":121,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲律師真係仆街<br />\n<br />\n比我就串鳩番佢收左警方錢先會埋沒良心咁幫黑警辯護，睇佢點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驛站原則(Cab Rank Rule)為法律界專業守則之一，亦稱不得拒聘原則，在這原則下，執業大律師接到案件後，除非存在利益衝突，否則若能處理該案件而當事人亦能付出適當費用時，大律師都必須摒棄對當事人或其訟因的喜惡，代其出庭訟辯。此原則可確保不會有人因為不受歡迎或因不得人心而不能覓得法律代表。</blockquote><br />\n個律師都無得揀客嘅<br />\n專業守則嚟<br />\n不過兜得樣衰囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"律師有律師既專業<br />\n醫生都有醫生既專業<br />\n<br />\n醫生既專業就係基於客觀既片段同medical record作出醫學判斷<br />\n<br />\n如果你敢挑戰我既專業，我都唔會對你既專業客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a68c59806a6bccff316d19390f8d32a308cacfe","tid":863434,"uid":61462,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":